caption: The satellite image sourced from GoogleEarth depicts a section of land bisected by a highway. The highlight of the scene is an overpass located towards the bottom of the image crossing over the highway. The surrounding area is a mixture of greenery with some trees and grass.

objects.referring_sentence: The object crossing over the highway towards the bottom part of the image is the overpass.
